content: today was a snowy day, i was very happy to see the snowflakes

visualPrompt.visualPrompt: A young child's hands cupped, gently catching a flurry of large, delicate snowflakes as they drift down from an overcast, softly glowing sky. The snowflakes glimmer and twirl, their ephemeral dance casting a sense of wonder and tranquility.
visualPrompt.colorPalette: Muted blues, grays, and whites with hints of soft, ambient light
visualPrompt.cinematicStyle: Intimate, close-up framing with a slow, gentle camera movement to emphasize the delicate movement of the snowflakes
